    b"     {{ _.role(\"system\") }}\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        You evaluate the conversation and produce"
    b" memory search hints for\x0d\x0a        the selected task.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        The hints will d"
    b"rive memory search before the selected task runs.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Stop once the hints"
    b" look good enough for the request without thinking about it too much.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a       "
    b" Search surfaces:\x0d\x0a        - tags: exact memory tags. They are not substring sea"
    b"rched.\x0d\x0a        - strings.contains: case-insensitive text fragments. Each value "
    b"is checked\x0d\x0a          as a substring against searchable memory content.\x0d\x0a       "
    b" - strings.equals: exact text values. Each value is checked for exact\x0d\x0a         "
    b" equality against searchable memory content.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Optional outputs availab"
    b"le in this step:\x0d\x0a        - candidate_memory: a vague remembered observation tha"
